description: There are 21 responses to this interactive game.  Responses are random. This is a great way to have two-way conversation with Alexa.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Funny Mommy to tell me a joke
Alexa, ask Funny Mommy to give me a knock knock joke
Alexa, ask Funny Mommy say a joke
name: FunnyMommy
shortDescription: This is a response type knock knock joke game.
